BodyParts3D LICENSE — verbatim record

================================================================================
ATTRIBUTION REQUIREMENT (Verbatim)
================================================================================

Every distribution of this data, derivative works built on it, and runtime
surfaces that display it MUST carry the following attribution string verbatim:

    BodyParts3D, Copyright(C) 2008 Life Science Database Center
    licensed by CC BY-SA 2.1 Japan

(The "(C)" represents the copyright glyph; ASCII-safe rendering. The Unicode
form "Copyright(c)" with the encircled-c glyph appears on the upstream pages.)


