================================================================================

Source of this license declaration:
    https://lifesciencedb.jp/bp3d/info/license/index.html
    (verified 2026-05-11 by the body project)

Canonical Creative Commons URLs:
    Human-readable deed (English):  https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.1/jp/deed.en
    Full legal code (Japanese, authoritative):
                                   https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.1/jp/legalcode.ja


